rComments: Lectures are very good; most of the information you are tested on comes straight from lecture notes. If you go to class it is an easy A.

Dr. Bay is the awesomest teacher ever!!!  He is the funniest teacher I have ever had.  All his lectures have been sooo interseting except one, which there was no way to make that material intersting.  As a teacher he was amazing.  His TA's are really good too.  His tests are very easy.  I would reccommend this class to anyone needing an easy gen ed
Makes class interesting.  Pretty funny as well...good lecturer.  Tests are pretty easy.  Learned a lot despite my lack of interest in subject.
Very funny guy! One of my favorite professors. He makes Latin fun (or at least bearable). He always pays attention to student concerns and explains concepts well.

HW is time consuming but read the book and practice the online quizzes and you'll pass. An A takes more work than a 2-hr credit might suggest but its possible. Bay is a very generous man, so ask him for help.
the class is easy because its online but the tests are very long and you have to know every single thing in the book. if you study its not bad but its very tedious

bay is great! his class is the hardest i'm taking this semester, but it's by far the most fun. he's a very straight-forward teacher and a really nice guy. he's very understanding if you have any problems and is even funny in class. i would definitely recommend his classes to other students.
